**Dues Payment**
----------------

Returning members are invited to pay their dues online. To check your dues status, go to the [Membership](/membership/) page and fill in your email address. Please go to the [Update Membership](/home2/online-membership-payment/) page to pay online. New members should complete the membership form (available [here](/home2/wp-content/uploads/2016/06/membership/Join2016.pdf)) and submit membership dues by check.

